description:
Danny recaps this week's Summer House, which featured hometown visits and a Luke/Kyle fight for the ages. After the Summer House recap, Danny is joined by RuPaul's Drag Race winner and Real Housewives of Atlanta super-fan Monét X Change to talk Drag Race, RHOA, and so much more!


Monét X Change: 19:15ish
